<div class="sub_visual">
    <div class="bg orora">
        <p class="title">고객센터</p>
        <p class="txt">내가 꿈꾸던 여행지를 현실에서 만나세요!</p>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="w1200 content_box">
    <div id="content">
        <div class="subpg_title_wrap">
            <h2 class="subpg_title">여행상품 Q&A</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="write_t_wrap">
            <a href="qna">목록</a>
        </div>
        <div class="answer">
            <h3>문의하시기 전 확인해 주세요.</h3>
        </div>
        <div>
            <ul class="imp_notice">
                <li>· 고객님의 소중한 의견을 빠르고 정확하게 해결하기 위해 최선을 다하겠습니다.</li>
                <li>· 예약한 상품의 취소는 카톡이나 Q&A를 통해 문의해 주세요.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <% if(typeof errs !== 'undefined') { %>
        <% errs.forEach(() => { %>
        <h3><%err.param%> : <%=err.msg%></h3>
        <%})%>
        <%}%>
                <form class="write_table" method="POST" action="newQna">
                    <table border="1" id="w_table">
                        <colgroup>
                            <col style="width: 18%;">
                        </colgroup>
                        <tbody>
                            <tr>
                                <input type="hidden" name="id" value="<%=row.id%>">
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>
                <span class="impt">이름</span>
            </th>
            <td>
                <div class="form_name">
                    <input type="text" title="이름" class="input_p name_im" style="width: 30%;" name="writer"
                        value="<%=row.writer%>">
                </div>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>비밀번호</th>
            <td>
                <div class="form_pw">
                    <input type="password" title="비밀번호" class="input_p" style="width: 30%;" name="pass"
                        value="<%=row.pass%>">
                </div>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>
                <span class="impt">제목</span>
            </th>
            <td>
                <div class="form_title">
                    <input type="text" title="제목" class="input_title" style="width: 100%;" name="title"
                        value="<%=row.title%>">
                    <div></div>
                </div>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>
                <span class="impt">내용</span>
            </th>
            <td>
                <div class="form_text">
                    <textarea placeholder="내용을 입력해 주세요." style="width:100%;" name="content"><%=row.content%></textarea>
                </div>
            </td>
        </tr>
        </tbody>
        </table>

        <div class="write_btn_wrap">
            <input type="submit" value="저장">
        </div>
        </form>
    </div>
</div>